There are many sections in JIRA where ordering of fields or content is accomplished by simple, fast, clear "drag & drop" operations (see the Configure Screen page, for example, as in the attached image).

Compare this with the method in which Favorite Dashboard order is handled (see other attached image) - this quickly becomes unwieldy and frustrating for a large number of Dashboards.

By using the more friendly, simple "drag & drop" method, this would be much easier to manage the order of large numbers of Dashboards.

