As a user, I'd like to have the ability to add a notion in my description or comments by team role or for the entire team. For example, currently when I add the notation @username or [~username], I can insert a username so they have attention called to them, and using my notification scheme, they get an alert. 

Often times I find that comments I've left on an issue are relevant to the entire team or a particular group of users within a project role. It would be great if I could alert them all at once by adding one such notation to my comment or other text fields within my issue.

